{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"split"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"separator"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Collection/Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sl7ElementQa","text":"Element"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"maxSplits"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":" = Int.max, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"omittingEmptySubsequences"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" = true) -> ["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Collection/SubSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sl11SubSequenceQa","text":"SubSequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The element that should be split upon.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"separator"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The maximum number of times to split the collection, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"one less than the number of subsequences to return. If","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"maxSplits + 1"},{"text":" subsequences are returned, the last one is a suffix","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the original collection containing the remaining elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"maxSplits"},{"text":" must be greater than or equal to zero. The default value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int.max"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"maxSplits"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"text":", an empty subsequence is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"returned in the result for each consecutive pair of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"separator"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"elements in the collection and for each instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"separator"},{"text":" at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the start or end of the collection. If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":", only nonempty","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"subsequences are returned. The default value is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"omittingEmptySubsequences"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of subsequences, split from this collection’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The resulting array consists of at most "},{"code":"maxSplits + 1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" subsequences."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Elements that are used to split the collection are not returned as part"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of any subsequence."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following examples show the effects of the "},{"code":"maxSplits","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"omittingEmptySubsequences","type":"cod